Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:05.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,To give me a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.73,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You want me to help protect\Nan entire empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.44,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It must be you, and you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But, what if I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.70,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Let's just say the empire isn't the only thing that's returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:25.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sparklriffic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:29.04,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,With Cadance putting all her strength\Ninto keeping her spell going,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:32.10,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,and me trying to keep an eye\Non signs of trouble in the arctic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:35.25,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,we haven't been able to gather\Nmuch information from the Crystal Ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There are Crystal Ponies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:38.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:42.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But I can't seem to remember anything\Nbefore King Sombra came to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,History of the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:49.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The last page of the book mentioned\Na crystal heart as the fair's centerpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,so I used my magic to cut one\Nout of a crystal block.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:56.27,Librarian,,0,0,0,,The whole purpose of the Crystal Fair\Nis to lift the spirits of the Crystal Ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:58.32,Librarian,,0,0,0,,so the light within them\Ncan power the Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.12,Librarian,,0,0,0,,so that the empire can be protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.45,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think we may have\Na problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it was an actual relic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:06.34,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,It's alright, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:07.83,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Twilie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.97,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,The empire is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.37,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I have to find the crystal heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, you stay here with Cadence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She needs you, Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll retrieve the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to figure out how I'm meant to pass Celestia's test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Retrieving the Crystal Heart must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:39.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But there is something else you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:43.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You and the rest of our friends have to keep the fair going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:43.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,With that... thing moving into the Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:50.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The whole purpose of the crystal fair is to lift the spirits of the crystal ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,so they can activate the crystal heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:57.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If the crystal ponies find out king Sombra is trying to take over the empire again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,their spirits are gonna be anything but lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It won't matter if I find the crystal heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You have to keep them happy here at the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:11.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Keep the fair going and the crystal ponies' spirits high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Done and done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:14.88,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Twily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.51,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:17.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:54.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I just found out they're offering face painting for the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,We can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight's doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.70,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,really... loves getting his face... painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Who wants a flugelhorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I want a flugelhorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Who else wants a flugelhorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I want a flugelhorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:23.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:26.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have to retrieve the crystal heart by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't lift a claw to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not a claw, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,So... Where are we going, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:43.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I might know where king Sombra hid the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,The Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The king would've been counting on the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that nopony would dare come looking for it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They would have been too afraid to even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You and me, both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Um, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be acting like nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:23.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should let me keep the crystal ponies away from the fake heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,while you show off your jousting skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Seeming my awesomeness does have a way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,of putting ponies into a pretty good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, Knight Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How are y'all feelin'? Having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The best I've had in over a thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Gotta renew that spirit of love and unity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.28,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,if you're gonna power up that Crystal Heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I sure would like to see it before the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hear ya, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Uh, gettin' a little toasty here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.46,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Bet you'd like to cool off with a little Crystal Empire nectar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Uh, you tried the crystal empire fritters yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Made from a traditional Crystal Empire recipy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You're gonna love'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I hear there's a jousting match about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna miss that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.02,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,These crystal ponies are more curious than a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's just gotta be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not a claw, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Celestia's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.69,Celestia,,0,0,0,,If the Empire is filled of hope and love,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.61,Celestia,,0,0,0,,those things are reflected across all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,If hatred and fear take hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,What? Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because this isn't king Sombra's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,Isn't this where he lived when he was in power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it didn't look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:40.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,When did you learn to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That was a little trick Celestia taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can you see what's down there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell how far down this goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:21.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can you see outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.18,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:34.98,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,Crystals!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Cadence's magic must be fading faster than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.63,Celestia,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I opened the door and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.66,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And now you must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.91,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.04,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You failed the test, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The test?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Not only will you not move on to the next level of studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.85,Celestia,,0,0,0,,you won't continue your studies at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:58.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I...You didn't say anything about no longer being your student if I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:01.77,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\fs12} Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.12,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twili-i-ight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know you told me to stay up there, but you were down here for such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,and you weren't answering and I got worried so I came down here and you were just staring at that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,I was calling your name but I couldn't seem to get you attention and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean... it's just a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:34.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ugh, how did I get...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,No! I don't wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please, Twilight, don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,King Sombra's dark magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:47.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A doorway that leads to your worst fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,We were home. You told me you didn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,You were sending me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A fear that will never come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna send you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I'm not gonna fail my test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:08.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Lots and lots of stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should come with me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:15.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Isn't there somepone else who can take over the jousting demonstration with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:21.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The faith of an entire empire rests on us showing these ponies a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:25.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But, you know if that isn't important to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:32.31,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'll take it easy on you next time but not too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I've got a reputation to maintain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,What if this is just more of his magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,He makes a door, that leads you to your worst nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,the one that is staircase, that goes on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hehe, excuse me, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:29.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of weaving materials for the traditional craftsbooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:33.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I just made a hat out of three pieces hay and a drinking straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I made it work, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We gotta do everything we can to keep this thing going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The Princess isn't looking so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:45.25,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I can imagine that her magic isn't going to last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,These ponies are gonna power up that Crystal Heart when the time comes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.03,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,and we won't be needing her magic anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I sure hope that time comes soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.18,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,even I can't keep this party going forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.44,Somepony,,0,0,0,,This isn't a Crystal Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The real one is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.57,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,On it's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:21.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I was going to say "...being polished", to buy us some more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.53,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,Crystal Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:35.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I actually studied gravity spells, thinking it might be on our test!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:39.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Turns out, I was prepared for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The heart! Where's the crystal…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:15.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Here! It rolled over to me when you dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can move, just not towards me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How could I've been so foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It was too easy to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Then when I saw what was going outside I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whe have to get out of there, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,You have to be the one who brings the crystal heart to Princess Cadance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you fail Celestia's test!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,King Sombra's already attacking the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He could reach the crystal ponies at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Reach Princess Cadance, my brother, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There may not be enough time for me to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You have to be the one to bring the Crystal Heart to the fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,Me? But Twilight…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:02.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:16.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Don't y'all worry your pretty crystal heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The real Crystal Heart will be here any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.36,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,He's back. I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.44,Somepony,,0,0,0,,King Sombra…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:42.66,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,My crystal slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey! Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have the Crystal Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.95,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,That is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Spiky-Wiky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.90,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Behold! The Crystal Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.45,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:41.12,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Use the light of love within you to ensure that King Sombra does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.59,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,What?.. No…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.75,King Sombra,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Good job, Spike…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I do so wish it was permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Did you see how my mane just absolutely sparkled?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But good things are better when they're a Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.70,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Everything's gonna be ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:15.04,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,You've gotta stop saving my rump like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.13,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,it's starting to get embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Was it me who saved you in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It was Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:24.78,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,It's just a test. Maybe she'll let you retake it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's gonna give me a new test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:36.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Keep it together, buddy... gotta stay strong... for Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.00,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I wish it had been me who ultimately made it self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.41,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Twilight, as I understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Spike brought Princess Cadence to Crystal Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:51.20,Celestia,,0,0,0,,because you weren't sure how quickly you will find a way to escape the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:55.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You weren't willing to risk the future of the citizens of the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.48,Celestia,,0,0,0,,in an effort to guarantee your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:02.51,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Far better that I've a student to understand the meaning of self-sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:05.79,Celestia,,0,0,0,,then one who only looks out for own best interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Does… this mean?..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,She's totally gonna loose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,Keep it together, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Gotta stay strong! For Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:30.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You were prepared to do your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:33.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,as one who takes to pass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.19,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All those doubts you can dismiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,turns out you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:42.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,prepared for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:45.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You clearly had what it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:49.47,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,To pass a test with such high stakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We knew for sure you would prevail,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:57.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Since when did Twilight Sparkle ever fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:01.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All those doubts you can dismiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,trust yourself and you cannot miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.68,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Turns out you were…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Turns out I were…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Turns out you were…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Turns out I were...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Turns out you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:20.95,Somepony,,0,0,0,,...prepared for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:25.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,I knew everything was gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:33.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVIY PONETC
